Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.18,0:03:40.28,IN_H_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,穿过茫茫无尽黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.85,0:03:45.61,IN_H_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,万丈曙光当可得见？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.22,0:03:51.08,IN_H_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,胸中铭记无数思念
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.19,0:03:53.22,IN_H_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,纵有苦痛亦有甘甜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.97,0:03:56.94,IN_H_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,回忆深烙于我心间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.55,0:04:00.18,IN_H_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,为了什么？　又是为谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.24,0:04:02.86,IN_H_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,本能将会如何作答？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.62,0:04:08.65,IN_H_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,挥出排山倒海一击
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.83,0:04:10.53,IN_H_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,你可听到？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.60,0:04:11.16,IN_H_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}灼热！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.08,0:04:11.79,IN_H_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.08,0:04:11.79,IN_H_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,内心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.32,0:04:13.21,IN_H_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,魂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.32,0:04:13.21,IN_H_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,灵魂
