Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.42,0:04:24.26,IN_H_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,执手相牵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.26,0:04:24.86,IN_H_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}烈焰！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.86,0:04:25.71,IN_H_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,给出答案
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.14,0:04:28.90,IN_H_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,为寻其中真意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.94,0:04:31.43,IN_H_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,旅途延伸无尽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.72,0:04:34.56,IN_H_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,罡风促我前行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.84,0:04:52.22,IN_H_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,虽曾立誓「相守不弃」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.82,0:04:55.04,IN_H_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,垂首却仅左右双拳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.34,0:04:57.35,IN_H_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,鞭长莫及又当何如？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.07,0:05:02.69,IN_H_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,惊恐万千亦不驻足
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.87,0:05:08.32,IN_H_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,残酷亦或铸就未来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.19,0:05:11.67,IN_H_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,下定决心这一瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.72,0:05:14.34,IN_H_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,我可依然仍是真我…？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.45,0:05:20.17,IN_H_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,如今又怎得暇旁骛…！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.47,0:05:22.02,IN_H_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,昂首向前
