Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.96,0:18:12.13,IN_N_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\3c&HFF0065&}向着明天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.13,0:18:13.19,IN_H_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,引吭高歌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.19,0:18:14.55,IN_N_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\3c&HFF0065&}向着世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.55,0:18:15.73,IN_H_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,引吭高歌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.20,0:18:18.88,IN_H_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,圣洁之风轻拂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.92,0:18:20.69,IN_N_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\3c&HFF0065&}晶泪随之飘却
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.83,0:18:21.79,IN_N_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\3c&HFF0065&}你我相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.00,0:18:22.91,IN_H_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,执手相牵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.25,0:18:24.26,IN_N_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\3c&HFF0065&}纵然跌倒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.32,0:18:25.48,IN_H_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,无畏向前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.65,0:18:27.48,IN_N_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\3c&HFF0065&}战栗弗休　毅然挺立
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.54,0:18:30.85,IN_N_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\3c&HFF0065&}坚定刻下　辉煌历史
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.96,0:18:32.55,IN_N_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\3c&HFFFF00&}纵此命陨却
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.67,0:18:33.79,IN_H_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,仍屹立不屈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.21,0:18:36.33,IN_H_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,让未来之花
